access: This listing is for the whole apartment. It's all accessible.
description:
Located right by Prospect Park and within three minute walk to either Q or B trains, one is within half hour train ride to downtown Manhattan or 45 min to midtown. The neighborhood features plenty of Caribbean eats and a vast park with many attractions.

Two large bedrooms with queen size beds. One small bedroom with a full/twin bed. Unfoldable couch in living room that can sleep two. All rooms are very bright with multiple windows. Two full bathrooms. Expandable dining table that can very easily accommodate 6 people. Elevator and laundry room in the building.

This listing is for the whole apartment. It's all accessible.

Owners will be abroad and available via AirBnB communication, email, text and phone.

Read what AirBnB has to say about it :)
https://www.airbnb.com/locations/new-york/flatbush

B and Q trains within minutes walking distance. Alternatively Uber or Lyft suggested.

hosts.about:
My name is Tomek. I’m a Polish native, however I’ve lived most of my life in Brooklyn and other European countries. I am 34 and work in the city in construction industry. Work consumes most of my time and when it does not, I try to keep in touch with friends and love to travel. Watching movies and series is my pastime. I read or listen to music when on the road. 

As both a guest and a host I use the space that I rent for the same reason as my own home – sleep. I am seldom indoors throughout the day due to work or sightseeing. When I’m in, I am quiet, considerate and keep the place clean whether it is as a guest or a host. I am a non-smoker.
